.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-LOCAL-RESERVE-PCT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-local-reserve-pct \- FEAT-2038 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-local-reserve-pct
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2038).
.PP
Computes the local reserve as a percentage of local balance per channel.
Returns 0 when local balance is zero.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
